metadata.name: Bunboclat
metadata.description:
Because it is nice to give back to the community, we have a Giveaway collection, allowing newcomers and adopters to grow the Buns fam.

Every bun owner will receive a digital alpha key (one drop per bun) to access to the incoming Next Decade App alpha. The app is the perfect place to bring NFTs together, no matter where they're from, and show your collection anywhere, anytime. Check our roadmap on Discord for more info on the App.

[https://linktr.ee/nextdecade](https://linktr.ee/nextdecade)
